    %% Data Flow
    DS1 & DS2 & DS3 & DS4 --> AF
    AF --> OV --> DC --> SL --> DB
    DB --> FEATURE_ENG & GRAPH_ENGINE
    FEATURE_ENG --> TRI_METHOD
    GRAPH_ENGINE --> ORACLE_XAI
    TRI_METHOD --> ORACLE_XAI
    ORACLE_XAI --> REPORT_GEN
    REPORT_GEN --> API_LAYER
    API_LAYER --> FRONTEND

    %% Config Flow
    CM -.-> FEATURE_ENG
    CM -.-> GRAPH_ENGINE
    CM -.-> TRI_METHOD
    CM -.-> ORACLE_XAI
    CM -.-> REPORT_GEN
    CM -.-> API_LAYER

